quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  22,1,Logo! Apnay perwerdigar say daro! Bilshuba qayamat ka zalzala boht hi bari cheez hai
  22,2,Jiss din tum ussay dekh lo gay her doodh pilaney wali apnay doodh peetay bachay ko bhool jayegi aur tamam hamal waliyon kay hamal girr jayen gay aur tu dekhay ga kay log madhosh dikhaee den gay halankay dar-haqeeqat who matwalay na hongay lekin Allah ka azab bara hi sakht hai
  22,3,Baaz log Allah kay baray mein batein banatay hain aur woh bhi bey ilmi kay sath aur her sirkash shetan ki pairwee kertay hain
  22,4,Jiss per (qazay-e-elahee) likh di gaee hai kay jo koi uss ki rafaqat keray ga woh ussay gumrah ker dey ga aur ussay aag kay azab ki taraf ley jayeg
  22,5,Logo agar tumhen marney kay baad ji uthney mein shak hai to socho hum ney tumhen mitti say peda kiya phir nutfay say phir khoon basta say phir gosht kay lothray say jo soorat diya gaya tha aur bey naqsha tha. Yeh hum tum per zahir ker detay hain aur hum jissay chahayen aik thehraye huye waqt tak reham-e-madir mein rakhtay hain phir tumhen bachpan ki halat mein duniya mein latay hain phir takay tum apni poori jawani ko phoncho tum mein say baaz to woh hain jo fot ker liye jatay hain aur baaz bey gharz umar ki taraf phir say lota diye jatay hain kay woh aik cheez say ba-khabar honey kay baad phir bey khabar hojaye. Tu dekhta hai kay zamin (banjar aur) khusk hai phir jab hum uss per barishen barsatay hain to woh ubharti hai aur phoolti hai aur her qisam ki ronaq daar nabataat ugati hai
  22,6,Yeh iss liye kay Allah hi haq hai aur wohi murdon ko jilata hai aur woh her her cheez per qudrat rakhney wala hai
  22,7,Aur yeh kay qayamat qata’an aaney wali hai jiss mein koi shak-o-shuba nahi aur yaqeenan Allah Taalaa qabron walon ko doobara zinda farmaye ga
  22,8,Baaz log Allah kay baray mein baghari ilm kay aur baghair hidayat kay aur baghair roshan kitab kay jhagartay hain
  22,9,Jo apni pehloo morney wala bann ker iss liye kay Allah ki raah say behka dey ussay duniya mein bhi ruswaee hogi aur qayamat kay din bhi hum ussay jahannum mein jalney ka azab chakhayen gay
  22,10,Yeh unn aemaal ki waja say hai jo teray hathon ney aagay bhej rakhay thay. Yaqeen mano kay Allah Taalaa apnay bando per zulm kerney wala nahi